#: ../../../using-the-compiler.rst:154
msgid ""
"All gas sent by default for external calls, previously a certain amount had "
"to be retained."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../using-the-compiler.rst:155
msgid "``spuriousDragon`` (*support deprecated*)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../using-the-compiler.rst:156
msgid ""
"Gas cost for the ``exp`` opcode increased, relevant for gas estimation and "
"the optimizer."
